description: 50 years ago, our founder Ken Curtis sparked a passion for Christian media. What started as Gateway films became what you know today, Vision Video. Take a quick look at the history of how Vision Video came to be and some of the many changes that have taken place. Thank you for 50 years and we look forward to the years to come.
